"    Tomotherapy system",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 360px; height: 354px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Tomotherapy system delivers radiation while rotating around the patient in a manner analogous to a CT scanner. Kilovoltage X-ray unit can be mounted on the gantry to permit acquisition of diagnostic quality CT images (one of the yellow beams in the image) or megavoltage CT can be acquired by capturing images in the treatment beam path. In serial tomotherapy, radiation dose is delivered to two adjoining slices before the couch is translated. In contrast, helical tomotherapy delivers dose during an arc rotation with continuous and simultaneous couch translation.",
